metadata.name: 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐋𝐎𝐍𝐄𝐑 #1
metadata.description:
Art is a form of creation that allows me to transcend or reinterpret reality, and to create unique universes that capture the imagination of an individual. 

I also like to think that Art can be an emotional language, allowing an artist to express his own feelings, or allowing an audience to share and feel a particular emotion.

I made this work to express some things that I feel deep inside me and that I don't want to talk about. 
Of course, I let you interpret this creation as you wish.

Enjoy 👽
